Generate a widget test for this LoginScreen. It uses AuthBloc. Test that it shows a loading indicator when state is loading.

```dart
class LoginScreen extends StatelessWidget {
  @override
  Widget build(BuildContext context) {
    return Scaffold(
      body: BlocBuilder<AuthBloc, AuthState>( 
        builder: (context, state) {
          if (state is AuthLoading) return CircularProgressIndicator();
          return ElevatedButton(onPressed: () {}, child: Text('Login'));
        },
      ),
    );
  }
}
```

Note: AuthState has AuthInitial and AuthLoading states.
